caption.p: HPLC-DAD chromatograms recorded at 269 nm of the mixed reference compounds: Gallic acid ( 1), mangiferin ( 2), caffeic acid ( 3), tectoridin ( 4), germanism B ( 5), irisolidone- d-glucoside ( 6), iristectorigenin B ( 7), nigricin ( 8), irigenin ( 9), 5,6-dihydroxy-7,8,3′,5′-tetramethoxyisoflavone ( 10), and irisolidone ( 11).
